OL,3,CMasked robber who threatened shop
OL,4,Cstaff with machete jailed
OL,6,FA masked robber who threatened shop
OL,7,Fworkers with a machete on two
OL,8,Foccasions has been jailed.
OL,10,FGary Walsh first entered the shop on
OL,11,FBrierley Road, in Blyth, at around
OL,12,F9.40pm on 26 July last year, having
OL,13,Fdonned a home-made mask and wielding a
OL,14,F21-inch long blade.
OL,16,FThe 33-year-old threatened two shop
OL,17,Fworkers with the machete and forced
OL,18,Fthem to hand over around #1,100 in
OL,19,Fcash before he fled the scene.
