OL,4,Cstaff with machete jailed
OL,6,FWalsh returned to the same premises
OL,7,Fsix days later at about 9.50pm, and he
OL,8,Fagain threatened an employee with a
OL,9,Fweapon.
OL,11,FOn the second occasion, the robber
OL,12,Fleft empty-handed but Walsh was soon
OL,13,Fidentified as the prime suspect.
OL,15,FIn a search at his home, the machete
OL,16,Fand clothing worn during the second
OL,17,Foffence were discovered.
