OL,4,Cstaff with machete jailed
OL,6,FWalsh, of Patterdale Road, Blyth, was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of robbery and
OL,8,Flater charged with one count of
OL,9,Frobbery, one count of attempted
OL,10,Frobbery and one count of possession of
OL,11,Fa bladed article.
OL,13,FHe was found guilty following a trial
OL,14,Fat Newcastle Crown Court in June, and
OL,15,Fwas sentenced at the same court last
OL,16,Fweek to six years and six months
OL,17,Fbehind bars.
