OL,6,FDetective Constable Ruth Herbert, of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police, who led the
OL,8,Finvestigation said: "Walsh's reckless
OL,9,Fdecisions on these two nights could
OL,10,Fhave easily had fatal consequences.
OL,12,F"He valued his own gain above the
OL,13,Flives of others, and I am pleased that
OL,14,Fsuch a dangerous offender has been
OL,15,Fhanded a lengthy custodial sentence.
OL,17,F"Walsh refused to take responsibility
OL,18,Ffor his actions, selfishly forcing his
OL,19,Fvictims to relive their traumatic
OL,20,Fordeals at court.
